{"title":"棉花老人","authors":["苏金伞"],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":8,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"棉花老人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏金伞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡下有个传说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说河西住着一个棉花老人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人家都说他是植棉能手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他自己却说是在放牧羊群。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他一到地里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那满地的棉花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像绵羊一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在他身边打滚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他抚摸着它们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和它们谈心；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他完全熟悉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的冷暖和性情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许多绵羊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合成大群，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而棉花也越开越多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变成满天的白云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他站在地头一望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白云舒卷着向他奔涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而他的弟子们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每人都驾着一片白云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其实这传说并没什么稀罕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这都是老人自己亲身的体验，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稀罕的倒是他的双手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的手毛主席曾经握过三遍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1956、8、3、于郑州"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}